Invocation Name: meet your army
des:
Meet Your Army is a monthly series of interviews by Dr. Rory Cooper the Director of Human Engineering Research Laboratories (HERL) with notable people serving in or attached to the United States Army.

For more information about the Human Engineering Research Laboratories (HERL), you can visit: www.herl.pitt.edu
The episodes from this podcast can also be accessed by visiting: https://www.herl.pitt.edu/education-outreach/meet-your-army
For questions or feedback please email us at apps.nitworks@gmail.com
